#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:10
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Working with the &kate; editor"
msgid "Working with the &kappname; editor"
msgstr "Arbejde med &kate;-editoren"

#. Tag: title
#: part.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Overblik"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:16
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The &kate; editor is the editing area of the &kate; window. This editor "
#| "is also used by &kwrite;, and it can be used in &konqueror; for "
#| "displaying text files from your local computer, or from the network."
msgid ""
"The &kappname; editor is the editing area of the &kappname; window. This "
"editor is shared between &kate; and &kwrite;, and it can also be used in "
"&konqueror; for displaying text files from your local computer, or from the "
"network."
msgstr ""
"&kate;-editoren er redigeringsområdet af &kate;'s vindue. Denne editor "
"bliver også brugt af &kwrite;, og den kan bruges i &konqueror; til at vise "
"tekstfiler fra din lokale computer, eller fra netværket."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "The editor is composed of the following components:"
msgstr "Editoren består af følgende komponenter:"

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid "The editing area"
msgstr "Redigeringsområdet"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is where the text of your document is located."
msgstr "Dette er hvor dit dokuments tekst er placeret."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:31
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "The Scroll bars"
msgid "The Scrollbars"
msgstr "Rullebjælkerne"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:33
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The scroll bars indicate the position of the visible part of the document "
#| "text, and can be used to move around the document. Dragging the "
#| "scrollbars will not cause the insertion cursor to be moved."
msgid ""
"The scrollbars indicate the position of the visible part of the document "
"text, and can be used to move around the document. Dragging the scrollbars "
"will not cause the insertion cursor to be moved."
msgstr ""
"Rullebjælkerne indikerer positionen af den synlige del af dokumentteksten, "
"og kan bruges til at bevæge sig rundt i dokumentet. Indsætningsmarkøren vil "
"ikke blive flyttet når man trækker rullebjælkerne."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:37
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "The scroll bars are displayed and hidden as required."
msgid "The scrollbars are displayed and hidden as required."
msgstr "Rullebjælkerne vises eller skjules som man vil."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Icon Border"
msgstr "Ikonkanten"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The icon border is a small pane on the left side of the editor, displaying a "
"small icon next to marked lines."
msgstr ""
"Ikonkanten er en lille rude til venstre for editoren, der viser en lille "
"ikon ved siden af markerede linjer."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set or remove a <link linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\">bookmark</"
"link> in a visible line by clicking the &LMB; in the icon border next to "
"that line."
msgstr ""
"Du kan sætte eller fjerne et <link linkend=\"kate-part-bookmarks\">bogmærke</"
"link> i en synlig linje ved at klikke med &LMB; i ikonkanten ved siden af "
"linjen."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The display of the icon border can be toggled using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Icon Border</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Visningen af ikonlinjen kan slås fra og til ved brug af "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Vis</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Vis ikonkant</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> menupunktet."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Line Numbers Pane"
msgstr "Linjenummer-ruden"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Line numbers pane shows the line numbers of all visible lines in the "
"document."
msgstr ""
"Linjenummer-ruden viser linjenumrene på alle synlige linjer i dokumentet."

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The display of the Line Numbers Pane can be toggled using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Line Numbers</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Visning af linjenummer-ruden kan slås til og fra ved brug af "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Vis</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Vis linjenumre</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menupunktet."

#. Tag: term
#: part.docbook:67
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "The editing area"
msgid "The Folding Pane"
msgstr "Redigeringsområdet"

#. Tag: para
#: part.docbook:69
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The folding pane allows you to collapse or expand foldable blocks of "
#| "lines. The calculation of the foldable regions are done according to "
#| "rules in the syntax highlight definition for the document."
msgid ""
"The folding pane allows you to collapse or expand foldable blocks of lines. "
"The calculation of the foldable regions is done according to rules in the "
"syntax highlight definition for the document."
msgstr ""
"Folderuden tillader dig at sammenfolde eller ekspandere blokke af linjer som "
"kan foldes sammen. Beregningen af områderne som kan foldes sammen udføres "
"ifølge reglerne i definitionen af syntaksfremhævning for dokumentet."

